Number 5:

54
00:01:52,170 --> 00:01:54,850
The Friend of My Enemy

55
00:01:54,850 --> 00:01:57,920
India and Pakistan don’t exactly get along.

56
00:01:57,920 --> 00:02:01,120
They’ve had four wars since 1947.

57
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,920
But fortunately for Pakistan,

58
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:06,340
