00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,270
back when no one wanted

62
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,740
to be the CCP’s friend.

63
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:12,900
You know,

64
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:15,420
because of all the mass murder.

65
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:16,840
Starting in the 1970s,

66
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,170
the CCP helped Pakistan

67
