82
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,150
Basically, Pakistan is India’s

83
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:48,350
biggest military threat.

84
00:02:48,350 --> 00:02:52,360
And the CCP is taking full advantage.

85
