141
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:34,040
And China’s belt is pretty high.

142
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:35,540
And as for Bhutan,

143
00:04:35,550 --> 00:04:36,970
the tiny, traditional nation

144
00:04:36,970 --> 00:04:39,590
that cares more about Gross National Happiness

145
00:04:39,590 --> 00:04:41,919
