153
00:04:53,830 --> 00:04:55,030
But the overall plan here

154
00:04:55,030 --> 00:04:56,810
is for China to have more influence

155
00:04:56,810 --> 00:04:58,070
on India’s neighbors

156
00:04:58,070 --> 00:05:00,800
