163
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:13,910
to subjugate India and indebt it to China
forever.

164
00:05:13,910 --> 00:05:16,950
But just because India is boycotting that
one initiative

165
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,411
doesn’t mean it doesn’t have

166
00:05:18,411 --> 00:05:20,780
economic ties with China.

167
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:23,160
India is already part of the Bangladesh-China-

168
