India-Myanmar—or BCIM—

169
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:27,100
Economic Corridor.

170
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,260
And earlier this month,

171
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:30,680
China’s National Development and Reform
Commission

172
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:33,010
