212
00:06:50,570 --> 00:06:51,889
Suffice it to say,

213
00:06:51,889 --> 00:06:53,750
Sri Lanka isn’t too popular

214
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,480
on the international scene—

215
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,330
