222
00:07:09,229 --> 00:07:11,330
But now, India also wants access

223
00:07:11,330 --> 00:07:12,740
to Sri Lanka.

224
00:07:12,740 --> 00:07:15,600
And it’s actively competing with China for
it.

225
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:18,020
India’s prime minister visited Sri Lanka
in May

226
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:21,080
