227
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,520
But then a few days later,

228
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,210
Sri Lanka’s prime minister went to

229
00:07:24,210 --> 00:07:26,610
the One Belt One Road Forum in Beijing,

230
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:29,919
